{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1N001018", "chronotag": "1761755113328", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "I-1018", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1018", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B1906", "triAmendement": "amaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaanmrnwo", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA608826", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845425", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Duby-Muller"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 3", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 3", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 3", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1906A.asp#D_Article_3"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "94", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 94"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00C0; la fin de l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;94, substituer au taux&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;2&nbsp;%&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">le taux&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;1&nbsp;%&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>L&#x2019;article 3 du projet de loi de finances pour 2026 pr&#x00E9;voit la mise en place d&#x2019;une taxe sur le patrimoine financier des holdings patrimoniales, dont le taux est fix&#x00E9; &#x00E0; 2%.<br>&nbsp;<br>Un tel taux pourrait aboutir &#x00E0; des situations d&#x2019;imposition sup&#x00E9;rieure aux revenus, et ce d&#x2019;autant plus qu&#x2019;aucun m&#x00E9;canisme de plafonnement n&#x2019;a &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; mis en place. <br>&nbsp;<br>Ainsi, une soci&#x00E9;t&#x00E9; d&#x00E9;tenant des immeubles financ&#x00E9;s par emprunt dont les loyers sont consacr&#x00E9;s en totalit&#x00E9; au service de la dette ne disposera pas de la tr&#x00E9;sorerie pour acquitter cet imp&#x00F4;t nouveau, correspondant &#x00E0; 50% de son chiffre d&#x2019;affaires, en se fondant sur une hypoth&#x00E8;se cr&#x00E9;dible d&#x2019;une rentabilit&#x00E9; de 4%.<br>&nbsp;<br>Il est donc propos&#x00E9; d&#x2019;abaisser le taux de ladite taxe de 2% &#x00E0; 1%.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-10-21", "datePublication": "2025-10-29", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9 apr\u00e8s publication"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1N001018?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}